                  "term": "Pouring funnel cake batter",
                  "termId": "cmppnma5j00007sv4md6buuc5"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " takes one attempt to get right. Use a wide pan so the cake has room to spread without touching the sides. Have the icing sugar ready: funnel cakes need to be dusted and eaten immediately.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
